join in for Oktoberfest.

05:22.191 --> 05:23.888
Yeah, I'll join in
from 10:00 till...

05:23.932 --> 05:27.414
Sober Oktoberfest.

05:27.457 --> 05:28.545
I'm trying to think...
maybe like a Corona.

05:28.589 --> 05:29.764
Yeah, of course.

05:29.807 --> 05:31.461
Can I get something
for you also?

05:31.505 --> 05:32.462
-Yeah, of course.
-Can I get a Tito's and tea?

05:32.506 --> 05:34.595
-Yeah.
-Mimosas?

05:34.638 --> 05:37.206
Will you please get a couple of
Coronas to the swim platform?

05:37.249 --> 05:39.382
And can we add
two glasses of champagne

05:39.426 --> 05:40.557
to that drinks order
as well, please?

05:49.000 --> 05:49.958
Sure.

05:50.001 --> 05:51.612
Z, be gentle.

05:51.655 --> 05:53.744
I thought that was your lady?

05:53.788 --> 05:55.267
