gonna see these people again.

06:02.927 --> 06:05.930
No, I know, but I think,
like, I just hate when you feel

06:05.974 --> 06:07.236
like you've failed at your job.

06:07.279 --> 06:08.803
I know, and I...

06:08.846 --> 06:10.195
That's exactly how I feel today.

06:10.239 --> 06:12.110
Honestly, I completely get it.

06:12.154 --> 06:14.461
It's hard, because
it falls on me, you know?

06:14.504 --> 06:15.940
Yeah, for sure.

06:15.984 --> 06:17.246
I'm doing my job.

06:17.289 --> 06:18.943
Yeah, it makes you feel
like sh--.

06:24.949 --> 06:26.603
