someone to, like, hype it,

08:25.809 --> 08:27.158
and I think you would be
the perfect person for that.

08:27.202 --> 08:28.159
Oh!

08:28.203 --> 08:29.813
This is awesome.

08:29.857 --> 08:32.076
I get to use some of
my skills of guiding people

08:32.120 --> 08:34.252
